<p>Associate Professor in the <a href="http://www.i.kyushu-u.ac.jp">Department
of Informatics</a> in the <a href="http://www.isee.kyushu-u.ac.jp/">Graduate
School of Information Science and Electrical Engineering</a> at <a href="http://www.kyushu-u.ac.jp/">Kyushu
University</a>. Also a member of PRESTO, Japan Science and Technology Corporation
since October 1999.
<p>Teaching and research interests include machine learning, logic programming,
combinatorics on strings, and analysis of algorithms.
<br>&nbsp;

-->

